OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,FA victim of one of the worst
OL,7,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,8,Fcriminal history has criticised the
OL,9,Fdeduction of up to #10,000 in legal
OL,10,Fcosts from his compensation for the 17
OL,11,Fyears he was imprisoned for a rape did
OL,12,Fhe not commit.
OL,14,FAndrew Malkinson was wrongly jailed in
OL,15,F2004 for the brutal rape of a young
OL,16,Fmother in Little Hulton, Salford, in
OL,17,F2003.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
