PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,FFollowing years of protesting his
OL,7,Finnocence, his conviction was quashed
OL,8,Fin 2023 after his appeal team forced a
OL,9,Fre-examination of evidence.
OL,11,FMr Malkinson has urged ministers to
OL,12,Fstop the "penny-pinching" over his
OL,13,Flegal fees and described how in effect
OL,14,F"he was having to pay for his own
OL,15,Fdamage assessment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,FHe said: "They insisted on structuring
OL,7,Fit such that I need experts to
OL,8,Fevaluate the damage done to me, and so
OL,9,Fnow they are going to deduct my
OL,10,Fexpenses for the experts, which could
OL,11,Fbe up to #10,000 under legal fees from
OL,12,Fmy compensation.
OL,14,FHe continued: "It doesn't make any
OL,15,Fsense at all to do that, except to say
OL,16,Fobviously they're trying to claw back
OL,17,Fas much as possible. They're penny-
OL,18,Fpinching.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,F"I think this is something that
OL,7,F(Justice Secretary) David Lammy could
OL,8,Ffix with the stroke of a pen tomorrow
OL,9,Feasily...
OL,11,F"It's really wrong, it feels
OL,12,Fvindictive. Why doesn't the state, the
OL,13,Fperpetrator of the injustice, pay the
OL,14,Fcosts for the experts and legal fees
OL,15,Fbecause they caused the damage, not
OL,16,Fme?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Ministry of
OL,7,FJustice said: "We know the grave
OL,8,Fimpact miscarriages of justice have
OL,9,Fand are committed to supporting
OL,10,Findividuals in rebuilding their lives.
OL,12,F"The miscarriage of justice
OL,13,Fcompensation scheme is designed to
OL,14,Fhelp individuals rebuild their lives
OL,15,Fand last year we increased the maximum
OL,16,Fcompensation payable by 30% to #1.3
OL,17,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,F"The Law Commission is currently
OL,7,Fconsulting on the law relating to
OL,8,Fcriminal appeals, including
OL,9,Fcompensation for miscarriages of
OL,10,Fjustice, and we will carefully
OL,11,Fconsider their findings."
OL,13,FDowning Street also pointed to the
OL,14,Fongoing consultation, with Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's spokesman telling reporters:
OL,16,F"Andrew Malkinson suffered a terrible
OL,17,Fmiscarriage of justice, and what
OL,18,Fhappened to him and the victim in this
OL,19,Fcase is appalling.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,F"Firstly, we're glad that the real
OL,7,Fperpetrator of this crime is now
OL,8,Fbehind bars, and we understand how
OL,9,Fgrave the impact cases like this have
OL,10,Fon those involved, and we're committed
OL,11,Fto supporting individuals in
OL,12,Frebuilding their lives.
OL,14,F"That's why we've increased how much
OL,15,Fcompensation is paid out after a
OL,16,Fmiscarriage of justice, making sure
OL,17,Fvictims are compensated for the crimes
OL,18,Fthey didn't commit and the years they
OL,19,Fcannot get back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
