PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,F"The Law Commission is currently
OL,7,Fconsulting on the law relating to
OL,8,Fcriminal appeals, including
OL,9,Fcompensation, and we'll carefully
OL,10,Fconsider their finding."
OL,12,FPaul Quinn, 52, was found guilty of
OL,13,Fthe 2003 sex attack on 17 April this
OL,14,Fyear after a six-week trial at
OL,15,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,17,FQuinn attacked a young mother as she
OL,18,Fwalked home in Little Hulton, Salford,
OL,19,Fin the early hours of the morning on
OL,20,FJuly 19, 2003.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
