CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779286285
OL,3,CWrongly jailed Andrew Malkinson claims
OL,4,C#10k deducted from his compensation
OL,6,FMr Malkinson, working as a security
OL,7,Fguard at a local shopping centre,
OL,8,Fprotested his innocence but was
OL,9,Fwrongly picked out at an identity
OL,10,Fparade and jailed.
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
